data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I found the site is Squarespace, with the official description, logo asset, booking URL, social profiles, and sitemap available. Next I’m pulling the sitemap, menu/contact pages, CSS, and the prototype seed so the concept keeps the current facts instead of inventing restaurant details."}

