handrarerestaurant/reservations/create/search?venues=richandrarerestaurant,pompetteau,darkshepherd,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\n>Open Menu<\n>Close Menu<\nhref=\"/menus\n>Folder:<\n>Menus<\nhref=\"/\n>Back<\nhref=\"/lunch-dinner\nhref=\"/lunch-specials\nhref=\"/lunch-dinner#banquets\n>Banquets<\nhref=\"/power-banquet\nhref=\"/the-experience\nhref=\"/functions\nhref=\"/gift-vouchers\n>Folder:<\n>Gift Vouchers<\nhref=\"/\n>Back<\nhref=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accent=0,0,0&accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&theme=light&venueid=10347%C2%A0\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\nhref=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&venueid=14196&theme=light&accent=157,157,157\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\nhref=\"/gallery\nhref=\"/contact-1\n>Folder:<\n>Contact<\nhref=\"/\n>Back<\nhref=\"/contact\nhref=\"/parking\nhref=\"/careers\nhref=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\n>Business Opportunities<\nhref=\"https://www.instagram.com/richandrare_brisbane/\nhref=\"#instagram-unauth-icon\nhref=\"http://facebook.com/richandrare.bne\nhref=\"#facebook-unauth-icon\nhref=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/richandrarerestaurant/reservations/create/search?venues=richandrarerestaurant,pompetteau,darkshepherd,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\n>LUNCH &amp; DINNER<\n>Artisan Sourdough Ciabatta (DFO, GFO)<\n>Bone marrow butter<\n>Wagyu & Foie Gras Crostini<\n>MB8–9 Stone Axe rump, onion chutney, horseradish cream & foie gras<\n>Wagyu Bites & Kiss Pepper Jam<\n>MB9+ Stone Axe chuck eye roll, panko crumbed<\n>Woodfired Bone Marrow (15cm)<\n>Served with pangrattato, chives and wagyu fat ciabatta<\n>Wagyu Kabayaki Skewer<\n>MB8–9 Stone Axe tri tip, served with burnt onion aioli, R&R kabayaki glaze & fried curry leaves<\n>Homemade Pork Sausage<\n>Mozzarella cheese, Calabrian chilli and Brazilian spices. Served with black garlic purée, paprika aioli and chimichurri<\n>Burrata (GF, VE)<\n>Pink peppercorn oil, black flake salt<\n>Jamón Ibérico (GF, DF)<\n>EVOO<\n>SNACKS<\n>OYSTERS<\n>Natural (6) (GF, DF)<\n>Lemon<\n>Mignonette (6) (GF, DF)<\n>Champagne vinaigrette<\n>Kilpatrick (6/12) (GF, DF)<\n>R&R hot sauce<\n>COLD SEAFOOD<\n>Caviar - 30g Kaviari Oscietra (GF, DF, GFO)<\n>Seafood Platter (Designed For Two) (GFO)<\n>Oysters (4), scallops, octopus, raw salmon, condiments<\n>Woodfired Beets<\n>Goat curd, hummus, black garlic purée<\n>Westholme Wagyu Tartare<\n>MB4–5 petit tender, yolk, fresh horseradish, homemade potato crisps<\n>Raw Salmon<\n>Ceviche, crispy sweet potato, salmon roe, green oil<\n>Stone Axe Wagyu Tataki<\n>MB8–9 rump, ponzu, wakame<\n>King Prawns<\n>Corn purée, homemade sweet chilli jam<\n>Seared Scallops<\n>Onion soubise, crispy jamón, charred peas<\n>Woodfired Camembert<\n>Roasted pistachio, pomegranate, caramelised onion, honey<\n>Woodfired Octopus<\n>Smoked hummus, confit lemongrass, pickled shallots<\n>MB9+ Wagyu Steak Tartare & Flintstones Bone Marrow (GF, DF)<\n>200g Stone Axe eye round, fullblood wagyu, 40cm bone marrow and pane carasau. Served tableside<\n>Woodfired Barbecue Pork Riblets (GF, DF)<\n>With bok choy, garlic shoots, homemade BBQ sauce, fried shallots and crispy garlic<\n>Wagyu Brisket & Burnt Guindillas (GF, DF)<\n>MB9+ L’Grow fullblood wagyu with R&R secret sauce<\n>Rich & Rare Triple Tataki (100g each) (GF, DF)<\n>With pickled ginger, ponzu, yuzu koshu, spring onion <\n>•Black Angus Rump Cap MB5+<\n>150-250 days grain fed, O’Connor Superior, Black Angus, Gippsland, VIC <\n>•Australian Wagyu Rump MB8-9<\n>•A5 Japanese Wagyu Rump Cap MB12+<\n>650+ days grain fed, 100% fullblood A5 Japanese Black Wagyu, Kagoshima, Japan<\n>ENTRÈE<\n>LARGE PLATES<\n>Market Fish<\n>Ask your waiter about our market fish<\n>Lamb Cutlet (GF)<\n>Baba ganoush, tahini yoghurt<\n>Crab Pasta<\n>Charcoal spaghetti, chilli, garlic, chives<\n>Truffle Mushroom Spaghetti (DFO)<\n>Charcoal spaghetti, mushroom ragu, porcini dust<\n>Half / Whole Live Lobster (GF, DFO)<\n>Lemon butter dressing, salmon roe, with one complimentary classic side of your choice<\n>À Piamontese<\n>Slow-Braised Stone Axe Wagyu Beef Cheek (DFO)<\n>MB9+ fullblood wagyu with truffle mashed potatoes, R&R special glaze and chives<\n>FROM THE GRILL<\n>Accompanied by a complimentary ‘Classic Side’ of your choice<\n>200g Eye Fillet<\n>AMH pasture-fed, grass-fed, Central QLD<\n>400g Scotch Fillet MB4+<\n>150+ days grain-fed, Riverina fullblood Black Angus, Riverina region, Southern NSW<\n>300g Sirloin MB4+<\n>270+ days grain-fed, Portoro Black Angus, British and Euro-bred Black Angus, Riverina region, Southern NSW<\n>600g Dry Aged Sirloin on the Bone MB4+<\n>200+ days grain-fed, 6 weeks dry aged, Black Angus / British bred, Yambinya Reserve, Northern VIC<\n>650g Rib on the Bone MB4+<\n>150+ days grain-fed, Ebony Black Angus, fullblood Black Angus, raised in the Western Downs region, QLD<\n>600g T-Bone MB4+<\n>270+ days grain-fed, Portoro Black Angus, British and Euro-bred Black Angus, Riverina region, Southern NSW<\n>500g Dry Aged Hereford Ribeye on the Bone MB4+<\n>28 days dry aged, 36 months 100% grass-fed, CopperTree Farms, raised near Foster, Gippsland, VIC<\n>Japanese A5 Wagyu<\n>Brand: Akune Gold <\n>150g Eye Fillet A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>150g Striploin A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>150g Rib Cap A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>150g Scotch Fillet A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>150g Rump Cap A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>150g Rump A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>150g Chuck Short Ribs (Boneless) A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>Australian Wagyu<\n>Accompanied by a complimentary classic side of your choice<\n>200g Wagyu Rump Cap MB6+<\n>500+ days grain-fed, Jade Pure Wagyu, purebred Japanese wagyu, Western Downs, QLD<\n>200g Wagyu Flank MB9+<\n>200g Wagyu Eye Fillet MB9+<\n>400g Wagyu Scotch Fillet MB4–5<\n>330+ days grain-fed, Westholme, Wagyu x Mitchell F1, Central Northern QLD<\n>300g Wagyu Scotch Fillet MB6–7<\n>300g Wagyu Scotch Fillet MB9+<\n>300g Wagyu Sirloin MB7+<\n","isError":false}

