data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_18","content":"<title>Lunch Specials &mdash; Rich &amp; Rare Restaurant Brisbane\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Dine between 11am and 3pm to enjoy mouthwatering lunch specials for under $30. \n>Due to severe weather warnings, Rich &amp; Rare will be closed for trade until further notice.&nbsp;<\n>SQUARESPACE_ROLLUPS = {};<\n>Static.COOKIE_BANNER_CAPABLE = true;<\n>Banquets<\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Open Menu<\n>Close Menu<\n>Banquets<\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Open Menu<\n>Close Menu<\n>Folder:<\n>Menus<\n>Back<\n>Banquets<\n>Folder:<\n>Gift Vouchers<\n>Back<\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\n>Folder:<\n>Contact<\n>Back<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Lunch SPECIALS<\n>LUNCH SPECIALS<\n>11am–3pm • 7 days<\n>Steak Sandwich   34<\n>Caramelised onion, horseradish cream, American cheese, fries &amp; peppercorn sauce<\n>Steak Frites   38<\n>MB2+ Riverina Black Angus Rump Cap (220g), fries &amp; mushroom sauce<\n>Barramundi  34<\n>Tomato coulis, smoked miso butter, pickled shallots<\n>Kids menu available upon request.<\n>10% Weekend surcharge (20% on public holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.<\n>OPEN 7 DAYS<\n>All Day Dining: 11:00am-late<\n>10% Weekend surcharge (20% on Public Holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.<\n>FIND US<\n>West Village Garden Pavilion<\n>97 Boundary Street,<\n>West End, Q 4101<\n>CAREERS<\n>Employment<\n>BUSINESS OPPORTUNITIES<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Subscribe<\n>Sign up to receive news and updates.<\n>Email Address<\n>Sign Up<\n>Thank you!<\n>Privacy Policy<\n> • Branding and design by <\n>Allo Creative<\n","isError":false}

