data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_19","content":"<title>The Rich &amp; Rare Experience &mdash; Rich &amp; Rare Restaurant Brisbane\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Beyond a banquet, this set menu showcases the best of the best. For an unforgettable dining experience, ask your waiter to suggest complementing beverages. From cocktails or whiskey to wines - the bar awaits.\n>Due to severe weather warnings, Rich &amp; Rare will be closed for trade until further notice.&nbsp;<\n>SQUARESPACE_ROLLUPS = {};<\n>Static.COOKIE_BANNER_CAPABLE = true;<\n>Banquets<\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Open Menu<\n>Close Menu<\n>Banquets<\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Open Menu<\n>Close Menu<\n>Folder:<\n>Menus<\n>Back<\n>Banquets<\n>Folder:<\n>Gift Vouchers<\n>Back<\n>R&amp;R Gift Voucher<\n>Tassis Group Gift Voucher<\n>Folder:<\n>Contact<\n>Back<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>R&amp;R Experience<\n>Beyond a banquet, this set menu showcases the best of the best.<\n>The menu • $220pp<\n>Artisan Sourdough Ciabatta<\n>Bone marrow butter<\n>Wagyu Tataki - MB8-9<\n>Rump, ponzu, wakame<\n>King Prawns<\n>Corn purée, homemade sweet chilli jam<\n>Westholme Wagyu Tartare MB4-5 Petit Tender<\n>Yolk, fresh horseradish, homemade potato crisps<\n>Scotch Fillet<\n>150+ days grain fed, Riverina, full blood Black Angus, Glen Innes, New England Tablelands, NSW<\n>Tajima Wagyu Striploin MB6-7<\n>Striploin A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<\n>650+ days grain fed, 100% full blood A5 Japanese Black Wagyu, Kagoshima Japan<\n>Red Wine Jus<\n>Bone Marrow Mash<\n>Green Beans<\n>Shoestring Fries<\n>Mixed Leaf Salad<\n>R&R Cheesecake<\n>ADD ONS<\n>Fried Egg <\n> Foie Gras <\n> King Prawn <\n> Whole Live Lobster <\n>240<\n> Blue Cheese <\n>10% Weekend surcharge (20% on public holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.<\n>OPEN 7 DAYS<\n>All Day Dining: 11:00am-late<\n>10% Weekend surcharge (20% on Public Holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.<\n>FIND US<\n>West Village Garden Pavilion<\n>97 Boundary Street,<\n>West End, Q 4101<\n>CAREERS<\n>Employment<\n>BUSINESS OPPORTUNITIES<\n>Business Opportunities<\n>Subscribe<\n>Sign up to receive news and updates.<\n>Email Address<\n>Sign Up<\n>Thank you!<\n>Privacy Policy<\n> • Branding and design by <\n>Allo Creative<\n","isError":false}

